data.description: Back on market-buyers no longer moving to SC! NEW ROOF! Prime location, all Brick, Updated & Top Schools! Conveniently located by hops & I20 (easy access to both 378 exit or Hwy 1 via Mineral Springs!) yet tucked back from all the hustle & bustle on a cul de sac street! This brick charmer, low maintenance home boasts TONS of recent updates including NEW paint throughout, NEW upgraded stain & pet resistant carpeting, completely RENOVATED owner's bath including luxurious oversized dual head shower, designer lighting & custom tile, 3-year young Trane AC, NEW lighting/ fixtures/ hardware, NEW marble counters in full baths, custom molding added & more! Upon entrance note all the details- plantation shutters, gleaming hardwoods, an abundance of natural light with an on-trend, semi open concept layout! Great room showcases gas fireplace, custom built-in bookshelf & French Doors leading out back! Spacious eat-in kitchen boasts granite counters, stainless steel appliances, bar seating with access to both dining & great rooms! Stunning dining room features new, custom wainscotting, soaring ceilings & oversized, picture window! Main level owner's suite offers a soothing color palette with walk-in closet & renovated bath with designer touches! Upstairs you'll find 3 bedrooms (2 with walk-in closets!) & guest bath with NEW marble counter/polished chrome finishes! Courtyard style, low maintenance backyard is the spot to relax or dine al fresco!
